{"tid":2411152,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"發唔發覺筲箕灣同港島其他地方完全係平行時空","createTime":"2021-02-17T06:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T01:20:35.000Z","uid":123613,"like":19,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9354c90fd83111dc6d34b1a60b1fc931407233e7","tid":2411152,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"藍色線本身比較少廢老 但黨鐵搭去柴灣方向 見到嘅廢老全部喺晒筲箕灣落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣落完車上到地面仲勁 尤其東大街嗰邊嘅出口 一出就成班廢老坐喺個公園仔 行多幾步又一大班廢老迫埋一齊喺菜檔買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前面個西灣河站一樣都多舊樓 坐多兩個站到柴灣都係多公屋 但氣場同筲箕灣完全唔同 筲箕灣名就係港島 實際同深水埗或新界牛屎地方分別唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5dd0d490104fe7eac4b036172a2c251253a70a","tid":2411152,"uid":225455,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"藍色線本身比較少廢老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去過北角未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44334206f4bbcbcbff013def086d6b3ee2c6cde","tid":2411152,"uid":215419,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"東區黎講除左杏花同太古之外 都好多廢老"},{"pid":"9402e6ee2801ef7cf3479e5872e8592038dfa4f4","tid":2411152,"uid":123613,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c44334206f4bbcbcbff013def086d6b3ee2c6cde","tid":2411152,"uid":215419,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"東區黎講除左杏花同太古之外 都好多廢老"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"筲箕灣多廢老不特止 連氣場都好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27be6c7b686918a0e1667cb8efc241f4186b3b5b","tid":2411152,"uid":248373,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:47:15.000Z","msg":"港島藍區重鎭係北角<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a